content:
Some products in Industries share features. In this release we’ve enhanced some of the features that help you provide excellent customer service, made updates that save you time in Business Rules Engine, extended functionality in Data Processing Engine, and much more.

Action Launcher:
Contact center agents can quickly resolve customer requests by launching Aura components.
Actionable List Members:
List creators can add or remove columns.
Default Record Status filter shows only active actionable list member records.
Bulk action configurations include OmniScripts.
Action plan templates allow assigning tasks to colleagues.

Business Rules Engine:
Incorporate new logic into expression set versions efficiently.
Map subexpressions’ variables to local resources.
Deactivate or modify decision tables referenced in expression set versions.
Use Has more than one million rows option for large row processing.
Save time with template creation and text comparison capability.

Context Service:
Use context definitions as a source for mapping data.
Generate and edit input mapping for all nodes and attributes.
Support different mapping types with mapping intent operations.

Criteria-Based Search and Filter:
Add Criteria-Based Search and Filter to Experience Cloud sites.
Visualize data by showing resources from search results in an interactive map.
Provide sorting options and share data from search results.

Data Processing Engine:
Upload large amounts of data into your definition with CSV files.
Use Data Cloud runtime for extended functionality on join, filter, formula, and writeback nodes.

Einstein Summary:
Quickly generate a summary of information stored in object records.

Grantmaking:
Create robust grant applications to help grant seekers save progress.
Track and measure the impact of grants with Outcome Management.
Ask grant recipients to report outcomes in Experience Cloud.

Industry Integration Solutions:
Deploy prebuilt industry integrations to CloudHub 2.0 shared spaces supported by MuleSoft Automation Services.
Choose to hide configuration parameter values during deployment.

Intelligent Document Reader:
Easily extract unstructured content and tables from documents, excluding unnecessary rows.

Intelligent Form Reader:
Easily extract unstructured content and tables from documents, excluding unnecessary rows.

Interaction Summaries:
Capture detailed notes of meetings and interactions using a single flow.

List Builder for Data Cloud Segment:
Suppressed records removed from a Data Cloud segment in associated actionable list.

Rollup Definitions for Record Rollups:
Streamline aggregation of records from various objects or groups.
Provide a consolidated view of your data.

Scoring Framework:
Build and deploy propensity models using clicks instead of code.
Define template configurations for scoring use cases.

Service Process Studio:
Integrate with Product Catalog Management to enable controlled access for service processes.

Stage Management:
Simplify complex business processes with greater visibility and control.

Timeline:
Configure a data graph in Timeline to show engagement events from data model objects.
Include event summaries on Timeline.
title: Enhanced Customer Service Features in Industries
